#### PR description:

Remove obsolete cfi's used for pre-V16 geometry versions of HGCal. The test beam application of visualisation will not work at the moment. The TB files are in transition and this will be fixed soon.

#### PR validation:

Use the test script in Geometry/HcalCommonData/test/python
